      "date": "2014-12-29 18:07:59.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nThis deletes *and* adds the file ldiskfs/kernel_patches/series/ldiskfs-3.0-sles11.series. Is that your intention? Should it be renamed to *sp2.series?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
