        "_account_id": 251,
        "name": "Bob Glossman",
        "email": "bob.glossman@intel.com",
        "username": "bogl",
        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2014-12-29 18:15:51.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nyes, that is the intention.  the deleted old version was a symlink. the new version is a whole file.  it's named sles11 instead of sles11sp2 for historical reasons.  that was always the name from before we did both sp2 and sp3.  no reason to change the name, if it's not broke don't fix it.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
